{"id": "jgs1665702758516", "title": "xmlvalidate", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "xmlvalidate"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgs1665702758516.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">xmlvalidate</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: xmlToStruct   \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: xmlToStruct   \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svz1665702699008.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: ProcScript: Functions \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: ProcScript: Functions \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rfg1665702624715.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgs1665702758516.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgs1665702758516.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgs1665702758516.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528868\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528868\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 06, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jgs1665702758516.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jgs1665702758516.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jgs1665702758516.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jgs1665702758516\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">xmlvalidate \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__xmlvalidate_251062\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Validate an XML stream.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__topic_d79997e1_d79998e1_d79999e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104jgs1665702758516_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__codeblock_ly3_znz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">xmlvalidate{/file}  XMLStream {,ValidationData}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__section_w2137ab1b7b5_w2138ab1b7_w2139ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d580860e66\">Example</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__p_d80003e1_d80004e1_d80005e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlvalidate/file I_XML, I_DTD</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__topic_d52662e1_d52663e1_d52664e1_d52665e1_d52666e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d580860e76\">Qualifiers</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7934e1_d7935e1_d7936e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Qualifiers</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7934e1_d7935e1_d7936e1__entry__1\">\n Qualifier\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7934e1_d7935e1_d7936e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7934e1_d7935e1_d7936e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/file</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7934e1_d7935e1_d7936e1__entry__2\">Treats <var class=\"keyword varname\">ValidationData</var> as a\n                        system path to a DTD file. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__topic_d52667e1_d52668e1_d52669e1_d52670e1_d52671e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d580860e123\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7937e1_d7938e1_d7939e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7937e1_d7938e1_d7939e1__entry__1\">Parameter </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7937e1_d7938e1_d7939e1__entry__2\">Data Type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7937e1_d7938e1_d7939e1__entry__3\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7937e1_d7938e1_d7939e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">XMLStream</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7937e1_d7938e1_d7939e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7937e1_d7938e1_d7939e1__entry__3\">\n Name of the field, variable, or parameter containing the XML stream.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7937e1_d7938e1_d7939e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ValidationData</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7937e1_d7938e1_d7939e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7937e1_d7938e1_d7939e1__entry__3\">\n Name of the field, variable, or parameter containing the validation rules to be applied to <var class=\"keyword varname\">XMLStream</var>; can refer to a Repository object, to a file, or can contain the validation rules itself.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__topic_d52672e1_d52673e1_d52674e1_d52675e1_d52676e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d580860e196\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlvalidate</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__2\">Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__3\">Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UGENERR_ERROR&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__3\">An error occurred</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1406</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_MEMORY&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__3\">Memory allocation failure</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1504</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UXMLERR_VALIDATE&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jgs1665702758516__table_d7940e1_d7941e1_d7942e1__entry__3\">An error occurred during validation of an XML\n                        stream</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__p_d80015e1_d80016e1_d80017e1\">Additional information is provided in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerrorcontext</span>, such as error messages from the XML parser.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__topic_d52677e1_d52678e1_d52679e1_d52680e1_d52681e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d580860e295\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__topic_d52682e1_d52683e1_d52684e1_d52685e1_d52686e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d580860e304\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__p_d80027e1_d80028e1_d80029e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlvalidate</span> validates an XML stream.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__p_d80030e1_d80031e1_d80032e1\">Validation objects (files, variables and so on) must follow the W3C Recommendations for DTDs. Furthermore, DTD objects should <var class=\"keyword varname\">not</var> contain the following items:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__li_d33596e1_d33597e1_d33598e1\">XML declaration (for example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\"?&gt;</code>)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__li_d33599e1_d33600e1_d33601e1\">Enclosing DOCTYPE declaration (in fact, DTDs that include a DOCTYPE declaration do not conform to the XML 1.0 Recommendation.)\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__p_d80033e1_d80034e1_d80035e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">ValidationData</var> is omitted, Uniface reads the DTD declarations embedded in the <var class=\"keyword varname\">XMLStream</var>. If no declarations are embedded in <var class=\"keyword varname\">XMLStream</var>, the parser reports a validation error.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__p_d80036e1_d80037e1_d80038e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">XMLStream</var> contains embedded element and attribute declarations and you also specify <var class=\"keyword varname\">ValidationData</var>, the XML parser receives multiple declarations for items in the stream. The XML parser reports a validation error in this situation.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__topic_d52687e1_d52688e1_d52689e1_d52690e1_d52691e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d580860e356\">Validation Data</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__p_d80042e1_d80043e1_d80044e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlvalidate</span> applies the following rules to distinguish <var class=\"keyword varname\">ValidationData</var>:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__li_d33602e1_d33603e1_d33604e1\">If the argument <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/file</span> is used, <var class=\"keyword varname\">ValidationData</var> is treated as a system path .\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__li_d33605e1_d33606e1_d33607e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">ValidationData</var> uses DTD syntax, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">xmlvalidate</span> treats <var class=\"keyword varname\">ValidationData</var> as a DTD.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__li_d33608e1_d33609e1_d33610e1\">Otherwise, <var class=\"keyword varname\">ValidationData</var> is treated as the name of a DTD stored in the Repository.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__p_d80045e1_d80046e1_d80047e1\">When <var class=\"keyword varname\">ValidationData</var> specifies a DTD stored in the Repository, use the following format:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__p_d80048e1_d80049e1_d80050e1\">{<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DTD:</span>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>.<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__li_d33611e1_d33612e1_d33613e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DTD:</span>—specifies that the XML stream is defined using a DTD (this is to ensure compatibility with future developments in the XML standard).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__li_d33614e1_d33615e1_d33616e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>—name of the DTD as specified in the application model.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__li_d33617e1_d33618e1_d33619e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>—name of the DTD's application model.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p exampletitle\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__p_d80051e1_d80052e1_d80053e1\">Validate an XML\n               stream</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Use the ProcScript statement <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlvalidate</code> to validate\n               an XML stream, even if the DTD for the XML stream is not in your repository.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The following operation \n\t <code class=\"ph codeph\">XVALIDATE</code> validates an XML stream using \n\t <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlvalidate</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104jgs1665702758516_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"jgs1665702758516__codeblock_wbw_14z_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation XVALIDATE\nparams\nnumeric I_STATUS : OUT\n string I_STATUSCONTEXT : OUT\n string I_DTD : IN\n string I_XML : IN\nendparams\n; I_DTD is a file path; use the argument /file\n; to indicate this to xmlvalidate.\nxmlvalidate/file I_XML, I_DTD\nI_STATUS = $procerror\nI_STATUSCONTEXT = $procerrorcontext\nend ; operation XVALIDATE\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gpq1665702699272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>XML Streams</a><p>XML streams are data streams using an XML format. They enable loosely coupled connections between components, and provide a standardized format for data transport between components. Uniface can transfer field data and data relationships via XML stream parameters. It can also attach processing information to data in an XML stream to allow the data state to be transported with the data.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528868\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528868\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "xmlvalidate Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 xmlvalidate Validate an XML stream. Explain this code xmlvalidate{/file} XMLStream {,ValidationData} Copy Example xmlvalidate/file I_XML, I_DTD Qualifiers Table 1. Qualifiers Qualifier Description /file Treats ValidationData as a system path to a DTD file. Parameters Table 2. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description XMLStream String Name of the field, variable, or parameter containing the XML stream. ValidationData String Name of the field, variable, or parameter containing the validation rules to be applied to XMLStream ; can refer to a Repository object, to a file, or can contain the validation rules itself. Return Values Table 3. Values commonly returned by $procerror following xmlvalidate Value Error constant Meaning -1 <UGENERR_ERROR> An error occurred -1406 <UPROCERR_MEMORY> Memory allocation failure -1504 <UXMLERR_VALIDATE> An error occurred during validation of an XML stream Additional information is provided in $procerrorcontext , such as error messages from the XML parser. Use Allowed in all component types. Description xmlvalidate validates an XML stream. Validation objects (files, variables and so on) must follow the W3C Recommendations for DTDs. Furthermore, DTD objects should not contain the following items: XML declaration (for example, <?xml version=\"1.0\"?> ) Enclosing DOCTYPE declaration (in fact, DTDs that include a DOCTYPE declaration do not conform to the XML 1.0 Recommendation.) If ValidationData is omitted, Uniface reads the DTD declarations embedded in the XMLStream . If no declarations are embedded in XMLStream , the parser reports a validation error. If XMLStream contains embedded element and attribute declarations and you also specify ValidationData , the XML parser receives multiple declarations for items in the stream. The XML parser reports a validation error in this situation. Validation Data xmlvalidate applies the following rules to distinguish ValidationData : If the argument /file is used, ValidationData is treated as a system path . If ValidationData uses DTD syntax, xmlvalidate treats ValidationData as a DTD. Otherwise, ValidationData is treated as the name of a DTD stored in the Repository. When ValidationData specifies a DTD stored in the Repository, use the following format: { DTD: } Name . Model DTD: —specifies that the XML stream is defined using a DTD (this is to ensure compatibility with future developments in the XML standard). Name —name of the DTD as specified in the application model. Model —name of the DTD's application model. Validate an XML stream Use the ProcScript statement xmlvalidate to validate an XML stream, even if the DTD for the XML stream is not in your repository. The following operation XVALIDATE validates an XML stream using xmlvalidate : Explain this code operation XVALIDATE params numeric I_STATUS : OUT string I_STATUSCONTEXT : OUT string I_DTD : IN string I_XML : IN endparams ; I_DTD is a file path; use the argument /file ; to indicate this to xmlvalidate. xmlvalidate/file I_XML, I_DTD I_STATUS = $procerror I_STATUSCONTEXT = $procerrorcontext end ; operation XVALIDATE Copy Related Links XML Streams XML streams are data streams using an XML format. They enable loosely coupled connections between components, and provide a standardized format for data transport between components. Uniface can transfer field data and data relationships via XML stream parameters. It can also attach processing information to data in an XML stream to allow the data state to be transported with the data. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}